OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVirgin Money to shut a     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthird of its bank branches 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Virgin Money will close 39 of its UK   
OL,6, banks as fewer people use bricks and   
OL,7, mortar branches and move to online     
OL,8, banking, the firm said.                
OL,10,FThe news comes after several High      
OL,11,FStreet banks including Lloyds and      
OL,12,FHalifax have shut branches.            
OL,14,FThe Unite union said "access to a bank 
OL,15,Fand cash is a fundamental need" for    
OL,16,Flocal High Streets.                    
OL,18,FVirgin Money said the closures amount  
OL,19,Fto a third of its banks and 255 workers
OL,20,Fwill be at risk of redundancy.         
